Mystic BBS DOOR WIKI for Linux

By Last Sysop MMXVIII

Before install read INSTALL

--=== Door help ===--

This is very first stage of development
Query from door program using:

wiki <keyword>

In case the sentence is supposed to be longer use:

wiki <keywords>

When the search is sucessfull the ansi program will
be called to display file in specified path.

At the ANSI viewer use <SPACE> to scroll a page and 
arrorws to eventually move up / down. Use <q> to quit
the viewer.

When on command line use "q" to quite to BBS.
Or wiki to search for a term.


